{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"init","kind":"keyword"},{"text":"?(","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sourcePosition","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/String","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":".","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/String/Index","text":"Index","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS5IndexV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"within","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"target","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"sourcePosition","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A position in a view of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"target"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"sourcePosition"},{"type":"text","text":" must be a valid index of at least one of the views"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"target"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"target","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The string referenced by the resulting index."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the index passed as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"sourcePosition"},{"type":"text","text":" represents the start of an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"extended grapheme cluster—the element type of a string—then the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"initializer succeeds."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following example converts the position of the Unicode scalar "},{"code":"\"e\"","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"into its corresponding position in the string. The character at that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"position is the composed "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"é\""},{"type":"text","text":" character."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let cafe = \"Cafe\\u{0301}\"","print(cafe)","// Prints \"Café\"","","let scalarsIndex = cafe.unicodeScalars.firstIndex(of: \"e\")!","let stringIndex = String.Index(scalarsIndex, within: cafe)!","","print(cafe[...stringIndex])","// Prints \"Café\""]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the index passed as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"sourcePosition"},{"type":"text","text":" doesn’t have an exact"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"corresponding position in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"target"},{"type":"text","text":", the result of the initializer is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":". For example, an attempt to convert the position of the combining"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"acute accent ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"\\u{0301}\""},{"type":"text","text":") fails. Combining Unicode scalars do not have"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"their own position in a string."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let nextScalarsIndex = cafe.unicodeScalars.index(after: scalarsIndex)","let nextStringIndex = String.Index(nextScalarsIndex, within: cafe)","","print(nextStringIndex)","// Prints \"nil\""]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["/documentation/swift/string/index/init(_:within:)-2u3iq"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/